Title Review: * Tips for life you will benefit if you apply them * * Rejoice with a little ... Even if a lot comes to you  you can know its value. * ... * Remember to be confident of yourself does not mean that you are conceited  but to trust yourself to the point that you belittle others  it means that you are condescending. * ... * The greater the amount of compassion with which you deal with yourself  the greater your ability to use it automatically in your interactions with others. * ... * There is no such thing as feelings of tension in this world  but human beings are the ones who think about things that make them nervous. *.
content: Tips for life you will benefit if you apply them     Rejoice with a little     Even if a lot comes to you  you can know its value          Remember to be confident of yourself does not mean that you are conceited  but to trust yourself to the point that you belittle others  it means that you are condescending          The greater the amount of compassion with which you deal with yourself  the greater your ability to use it automatically in your interactions with others          There is no such thing as feelings of tension in this world  but human beings are the ones who think about things that make them nervous
